description: LAST UNIT AVAILABLE! Welcome to 9 Glover Court - South Boston's newest and most exciting boutique elevator building comprised of 7 brand new, thoughtfully designed homes. Unit 2 features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, outfitted in carefully curated finishes for the most discerning of buyers. In the front of the unit sits your primary suite complete with en-suite bathroom and fully built-out walk in closet and 1 of 2 private outdoor spaces. Down the hall you'll find your additional bedrooms and 2nd full bath. Towards the back of the home is your expansive and open kitchen and living space. The kitchen boasts two-tone shaker cabinets w/ white uppers and blue lowers, Thermador appliances and quartz counters. Enjoy your 2nd private outdoor space right off of the living room just in time for summer and fall. Common turfed backyard! One garage parking spot and additional private storage are included. Located in an area of Southie that is slated for redevelopment and transformation!
